HDP USA

Dta v sbore gnpUSA.txt predstavuj asov rad zachytvajci rast HDP v Spojench ttoch americkch tvrrone v obdob druh kvartl 1947 do prvho kvartlu 1991. (gross national product)

loha: Urobte predikciu rastu HDP na zvyn tri kvartly roku 1991 a zhodnote.

1. Zobrazme asov rad a slovne popeme

Natanie dt

gnpUSA <- read.table("gnpUSA.txt", quote="\"", comment.char="")
str(gnpUSA)
## 'data.frame':    176 obs. of  1 variable:
##  $ V1: num  0.00632 0.00366 0.01202 0.00627 0.01761 ...
GNP<-gnpUSA$V1

Zobrazenie dt

gnp<-ts(GNP, start=c(1947,2),frequency=4)
plot(gnp,type="o",col="blue", main = "Rast HDP v Spojench ttoch americkch
tvrrone v obdob druh kvartl 1947 do prvho kvartlu 1991.")
abline(0,0)

Pozorovanie

  • kontantn nenulov trend
  • ustlen variabilita

2. Njdeme tento trend a odstrnime ho, aby sme dostali rezidu.

Ako? Diferencovanm, regresiou. Vyberieme si regresiu.

ahko sa d ukza, e metdou najmench tvorcov dostaneme trend rovn priemeru.

c<-mean(gnp)
c
## [1] 0.00774125
rezidua<-gnp-mean(gnp)
plot(rezidua, type="o",col="red")
abline(0,0)

Zver: \[X(t)=0,0077+Y(t)\]

V prpade kontantnho trendu vak netreba odstraova tento trend v R, pretoe prkazy vedia pracova s touto kontantou. Mono pracova priamo s pvodnm radom, ktor je u stacionrny.

3. Hadanie modelu pre \(X(t)\)

Vyuijeme identifikciu modelu pomocou ACF a PACF

acf(rezidua, 40)

pacf(rezidua, 40)

Poda ACF MA(2) a poda PACF AR(1) - volme ten s menm potom parametrov(princp spornosti). Model teda hadme v tvare: \[X(t) - \mu = \phi X(t-1) + Z(t),\] kde \(Z(t) \sim WN(0,\sigma^2)\).

# ar.ols(gnp, order.max = 1) # minule sme pouzili toto - metoda najmensich stvorcov
m1 = ar.mle(gnp, order = 1) # metoda maximalnej vierohodnosti
m1
## 
## Call:
## ar.mle(x = gnp, order.max = 1)
## 
## Coefficients:
##      1  
## 0.3786  
## 
## Order selected 1  sigma^2 estimated as  9.801e-05

Je toto dostaton? Mali by sme sa pozrie na rezidu. Je uiton pouva prkaz names - vype vetky premenn uloen v objekte.

names(m1)
##  [1] "order"        "ar"           "var.pred"     "x.mean"      
##  [5] "aic"          "n.used"       "order.max"    "partialacf"  
##  [9] "resid"        "method"       "series"       "frequency"   
## [13] "call"         "asy.var.coef"
plot(m1$resid, main='Rezidu modelu',type='o')
abline(0,0)

Alternatvne mono na modelovanie poui aj prkaz ARIMA:

m2 = arima(gnp, order=c(1,0,0), method = 'ML')
names(m2)
##  [1] "coef"      "sigma2"    "var.coef"  "mask"      "loglik"   
##  [6] "aic"       "arma"      "residuals" "call"      "series"   
## [11] "code"      "n.cond"    "nobs"      "model"
plot(m2$residuals, main='Rezidu modelu',type='o')
abline(0,0)

Dostvame rovnak model. Overme sprvnos.

resM1 = m1$resid[2:length(m1$resid)]
acf(resM1,40)

pacf(resM1,40)

Box.test(resM1)
## 
##  Box-Pierce test
## 
## data:  resM1
## X-squared = 0.41039, df = 1, p-value = 0.5218
Box.test(resM1, type='Ljung')
## 
##  Box-Ljung test
## 
## data:  resM1
## X-squared = 0.41747, df = 1, p-value = 0.5182

Poda ACF a PACF s nezvisl a Box testy tie nezamietaj hypotzu o nezvislosti, take sme zvolili dobr model \(X(t) = 0.0077+0.38X(t-1)+Z(t)\). \(Z(t)\) mono povaova za biely um s parametrami

4. Odhadneme koeficienty modelu

Ako? Metdy OLS, MLE, Yule-Walker pre AR proces. V R to vie urobi prkaz ar, resp. arima, kee ar je pecilny prpad arima. Vyskame metdu mle.

5. Overenie sprvnosti modelu

6. Predikcia budcich hodnt (pre 3 nasledujce kvartly)

Napr. pomocou BLUP.

m1pred = predict(m1, n.ahead=3)
m1pred
## $pred
##             Qtr2        Qtr3        Qtr4
## 1991 0.002348909 0.005699257 0.006967756
## 
## $se
##             Qtr2        Qtr3        Qtr4
## 1991 0.009899883 0.010585706 0.010680411

7. Grafick znzornenie predikcie

PR = m1pred$pred
CH = m1pred$se

H = PR + 1.96*CH
D = PR - 1.96*CH

h = ts(H, start=c(1991,2), frequency = 4)
d = ts(D, start=c(1991,2), frequency = 4)
pr = ts(PR, start=c(1991,2), frequency = 4)
plot(gnp)
lines(pr, col = 'blue')
lines(h, col = 'red')
lines(d, col = 'red')

LEP MODEL - IDENTIFIKCIA pomocou Akaikeho informanho kritria (nie pomocou ACF), o je tatistika istho tvaru, priom R-excel prejde cez vetky mon AR modely. Riadi sa pri tom jednm z bodov Okhamovej britvy, t.j. vyberie model s najmenm rozptylom bieleho umu.

3. - 4. Odhalenie modelu a jeho koeficientov
